dc_title_s: Development Areas, Chesapeake Bay Critical Area Program: Prince George's County, Maryland, 1988
dc_description_s: The locations where development is subject to the requirements of not only the Zoning Ordinance, Subtitle 27, but also the regulations found in the Prince George's County Chesapeake Bay Critical Area Program Conservation Manual for environmentally sensitive property located in Prince George's County, Maryland.
dc_creator_sm: The Maryland-National Capital Park & Planning Commission
